WEBVTT

00:01:08.465 --> 00:01:10.905
Why don't we reschedule for next week?

00:01:10.985 --> 00:01:13.185
That's good. I haven't told the staff yet.

00:01:13.265 --> 00:01:15.425
I'm worried
they won't be able to process it.

00:01:16.025 --> 00:01:18.025
Get Ms. Lin to change her mind
and rent somewhere else.

00:01:19.825 --> 00:01:20.665
A ghost!

00:01:20.745 --> 00:01:24.025
You should be talking to Mr. Pao
to find new opportunities for the staff

00:01:24.105 --> 00:01:27.705
instead of plotting immature tricks
like a woman-child.

00:01:27.785 --> 00:01:29.585
I need to change my plan.

00:01:29.665 --> 00:01:31.945
Is our secret group's name adorable?

00:01:32.025 --> 00:01:33.745
The CEO has been reeled in.

00:01:47.025 --> 00:01:49.025
Can you tell me now what happened?

00:01:55.865 --> 00:01:57.985
What were you so afraid of,
shaking that much?

00:02:03.265 --> 00:02:04.505
There was a cockroach.

00:02:06.905 --> 00:02:08.065
A cockroach?

00:02:09.425 --> 00:02:10.265
Mhm.

00:02:11.144 --> 00:02:13.105
You're not afraid,
so you wouldn't understand.

00:02:13.185 --> 00:02:14.945
I'm lucky I didn't faint.

00:02:18.105 --> 00:02:20.585
But thank you so much for saving me.

00:02:22.025 --> 00:02:24.905
So what are you doing here?

00:02:26.705 --> 00:02:28.145
I'm here to see you.

00:02:29.905 --> 00:02:31.385
I wanted to ask you something.

00:02:33.745 --> 00:02:34.585
What is it?

00:02:36.705 --> 00:02:40.065
Do you know who sent me the balloons
and pure iced matcha?

00:02:45.025 --> 00:02:46.385
I'll find out for you.

00:02:49.025 --> 00:02:51.865
If you see her, tell her I appreciate it.

00:02:57.905 --> 00:03:00.145
I love pure iced matcha.

00:03:02.425 --> 00:03:03.665
No sugar.

00:03:09.505 --> 00:03:11.225
Who would buy it for you?

00:03:51.905 --> 00:03:54.865
Someone hung the balloons
at the gate again, ma'am.

00:04:08.745 --> 00:04:10.065
Donut.

00:04:11.185 --> 00:04:16.425
I can't believe I finally found
the one who makes me smile.

00:04:16.504 --> 00:04:17.504
Hm?

00:04:19.384 --> 00:04:22.105
That was quite a shock
we just had, wasn't it?

00:04:26.505 --> 00:04:30.225
So who really was the first one to flirt?

00:04:31.345 --> 00:04:32.225
Who do you think it was?

00:04:33.905 --> 00:04:35.225
Me?

00:04:39.625 --> 00:04:41.705
I'll introduce you to Ms. Lin someday.

00:04:42.385 --> 00:04:44.545
You'll like her a lot.

00:04:50.585 --> 00:04:51.905
However,

00:04:52.905 --> 00:04:55.305
our livelihood is more important.

00:04:56.225 --> 00:04:59.785
I need to stick to the plan
and not get soft, right?

00:05:00.385 --> 00:05:01.425
Yeah?

00:05:12.705 --> 00:05:14.865
When did you even order it, ma'am?

00:05:16.545 --> 00:05:18.265
Should I order one for you tomorrow?

00:05:19.385 --> 00:05:20.545
It's okay.

00:05:22.385 --> 00:05:23.385
Alright.

00:05:33.225 --> 00:05:34.425
It's refreshing.

00:05:40.385 --> 00:05:41.385
So sweet.

00:05:42.585 --> 00:05:46.025
Sweet? But that's pure iced matcha.

00:05:47.265 --> 00:05:49.465
Perfectly bitter.

00:05:59.025 --> 00:06:00.345
-I'll come back to help.
-Okay.

00:06:05.225 --> 00:06:06.385
Hello.

00:06:10.665 --> 00:06:12.505
Is that the Japanese restaurant?

00:06:13.105 --> 00:06:14.705
Who are you trying to call?

00:06:15.465 --> 00:06:17.905
I'm sorry. I called the wrong number.

00:06:19.985 --> 00:06:21.825
How many times a day
is this going to happen?

00:06:24.545 --> 00:06:26.585
I kept trying to call other numbers,

00:06:27.185 --> 00:06:28.865
but I ended up calling this one.

00:06:32.305 --> 00:06:34.385
Maybe I should block your number.

00:06:34.465 --> 00:06:37.425
Block it, ma'am.
Definitely a scammer, calling you all day.

00:06:37.505 --> 00:06:39.625
Where did they even get your number?

00:06:43.425 --> 00:06:44.705
Oh, I almost forgot.

00:06:44.785 --> 00:06:47.025
After the meeting, we have work to do.

00:07:07.945 --> 00:07:09.865
Oh, Ms. Lin?

00:07:11.985 --> 00:07:14.465
I'm sorry. I was in meetings all day.

00:07:14.545 --> 00:07:15.825
Mhm.

00:07:15.905 --> 00:07:17.025
Are you tired?

00:07:17.825 --> 00:07:20.145
More hungry than tired, so I came over.

00:07:20.225 --> 00:07:22.625
Oh? Then why didn't you call
to order from me?

00:07:23.785 --> 00:07:24.945
I blocked your number.

00:07:28.345 --> 00:07:29.625
I'd rather see your face.

00:07:50.065 --> 00:07:51.785
I can't believe

00:07:51.865 --> 00:07:57.025
that a big company like Family Nest
have a female executive this young.

00:08:05.505 --> 00:08:08.505
I took over for my father
just a little while ago.

00:08:09.185 --> 00:08:11.905
Why? Is your father retired?

00:08:11.985 --> 00:08:15.385
Not really. He's not feeling well.

00:08:15.465 --> 00:08:17.225
He's dealing with ALS right now.

00:08:17.825 --> 00:08:18.825
Oh.

00:08:18.905 --> 00:08:20.545
So your father took a break

00:08:21.105 --> 00:08:23.945
and let his daughter
run the company in his place.

00:08:26.785 --> 00:08:29.505
I know it's a little too soon,
but I want to give it a try.

00:08:30.065 --> 00:08:31.905
I'm worried about him,
and want him to relax.

00:08:34.345 --> 00:08:36.705
But I don't really know
how long I can keep going.

00:08:36.784 --> 00:08:37.985
Why?

00:08:38.505 --> 00:08:40.664
The partners don't seem
to have much faith in me.

00:08:43.305 --> 00:08:46.345
The tutoring school project
that's going to be at Play Park's location

00:08:46.425 --> 00:08:48.945
is a chance to prove my capability.

00:08:51.665 --> 00:08:52.665
If it doesn't work out,

00:08:53.545 --> 00:08:57.865
or the performance is lacking,
they'll vote for a new executive.

00:08:58.945 --> 00:09:01.785
Maybe Dad would have to
get back in the position.

00:09:03.465 --> 00:09:07.305
So I'm putting my all into this project
and don't plan to disappoint Dad,

00:09:08.265 --> 00:09:10.585
so he won't need to
go back to stressful work

00:09:11.305 --> 00:09:12.745
and risk relapsing.

00:09:49.705 --> 00:09:52.145
Sorry for only talking
about stressful stuff.

00:09:52.225 --> 00:09:53.105
Did I bore you?

00:09:54.585 --> 00:09:56.945
Not at all. I'm a good listener.

00:09:57.025 --> 00:09:58.665
When it comes to your stories,

00:09:58.745 --> 00:10:01.145
I love to listen
and I want to know everything.

00:10:04.065 --> 00:10:06.425
I know you really love Play Park.

00:10:06.505 --> 00:10:09.545
It's not just a workplace.
A deep bond has been created.

00:10:14.345 --> 00:10:16.985
In the past few days,
you've been trying to indulge me

00:10:17.065 --> 00:10:19.865
because you've learned what I like, right?

00:10:23.905 --> 00:10:25.785
I think I've figured out your game plan.

00:10:26.425 --> 00:10:28.785
You're trying to change my mind.

00:10:36.265 --> 00:10:39.025
I admit, I'm really into you.

00:10:42.825 --> 00:10:44.265
But I'm not mad at you.

00:10:45.025 --> 00:10:47.545
It's been an enjoyable few days.

00:10:47.625 --> 00:10:48.465
It's not lonely.

00:10:52.585 --> 00:10:56.385
If this all ends one day,
I'll feel quite lost.

00:11:40.065 --> 00:11:41.625
-Let's go.
-Yeah.

00:12:09.185 --> 00:12:10.785
Why are you yelling?!

00:12:11.425 --> 00:12:13.105
Who told you to sleep here?

00:12:13.745 --> 00:12:15.505
And why did you come down here?

00:12:15.585 --> 00:12:17.185
Why aren't you sleeping?

00:12:22.905 --> 00:12:24.185
I'm thirsty.

00:12:26.905 --> 00:12:28.465
What's keeping you awake this time?

00:12:31.905 --> 00:12:33.105
It's Play Park, isn't it?

00:12:38.585 --> 00:12:39.825
I've decided.

00:12:50.945 --> 00:12:54.345
You promised
that no one would lose their job.

00:12:54.945 --> 00:12:56.665
I won't go back on my promise.

00:12:57.665 --> 00:13:00.985
I'm relieved that you
and the staff have come to terms with it.

00:13:06.025 --> 00:13:07.985
Thank you so much for understanding us.

00:13:09.385 --> 00:13:11.545
I understand you as well.

00:13:12.465 --> 00:13:14.785
Everyone has their own needs.

00:13:17.465 --> 00:13:18.665
I'm sorry

00:13:19.345 --> 00:13:21.705
for not being able
to keep Play Park running.

00:13:23.905 --> 00:13:25.225
It's okay, Mr. Pao.

00:13:25.865 --> 00:13:28.505
Just helping us find new jobs
is really kind of you.

00:13:38.225 --> 00:13:41.625
-Yes, Ms. Lin?
-Let's go to Play Park this afternoon.

00:13:41.705 --> 00:13:43.585
Mr. Pao has decided
to let us rent the place.

00:13:44.185 --> 00:13:45.025
Really?

00:13:57.385 --> 00:13:59.465
Kids, are you ready to board the train?

00:13:59.545 --> 00:14:00.465
-I'm ready.
-I'm ready.

00:14:00.545 --> 00:14:01.865
Raise your hand if you're ready.

00:14:01.945 --> 00:14:04.345
Okay, then stand up!

00:14:04.425 --> 00:14:07.505
Come on. Put your hands on the shoulders
in front of you to form the train.

00:14:08.105 --> 00:14:10.025
Good job! Let's go.

00:14:10.625 --> 00:14:12.265
Moms and Dads, please join us.

00:14:12.345 --> 00:14:14.545
Come on, come on.

00:14:14.625 --> 00:14:18.625
We're boarding the train now.
What sound does the train make?

00:14:18.705 --> 00:14:21.505
-Choo choo! Good job.
-Choo choo!

00:14:25.945 --> 00:14:27.625
Well, are you ready?

00:14:27.705 --> 00:14:28.545
I'm ready.

00:14:28.625 --> 00:14:31.865
The train is moving now.

00:14:31.945 --> 00:14:33.545
What sound does the train make again?

00:14:33.625 --> 00:14:35.985
-Choo choo!
-Choo choo!

00:14:36.065 --> 00:14:37.105
What's the sound?

00:14:37.185 --> 00:14:39.505
Choo choo! Good job.

00:14:41.945 --> 00:14:44.825
-What world are we going into?
-Octopus!

00:14:44.905 --> 00:14:46.185
An octopus.

00:14:46.265 --> 00:14:47.185
Dinosaurs!

00:14:47.265 --> 00:14:49.905
Dinosaurs. What color are they?

00:14:49.985 --> 00:14:51.345
This one is pink.

00:14:51.425 --> 00:14:53.625
And blue, and orange.

00:14:55.345 --> 00:14:57.225
It's hiding in the water.

00:14:57.305 --> 00:15:00.025
It's in the water?
An octopus has tentacles. What does it do?

00:15:00.105 --> 00:15:02.465
Like this?

00:15:19.225 --> 00:15:21.385
Hey, we're arriving at the gate

00:15:21.465 --> 00:15:25.545
where we have to sing together
for it to open again.

00:15:25.625 --> 00:15:26.785
Are you ready?

00:15:26.865 --> 00:15:29.865
If not, we'll be stuck here
and won't be able to enter.

00:15:29.945 --> 00:15:30.905
Let's sing. One, two, three.

00:15:31.505 --> 00:15:36.465
‎Quack, quack, quack!
‎The ducks are bathing in the canal

00:15:36.545 --> 00:15:41.865
‎Eyes wide open,
‎looking at the fish and shrimp

00:15:41.945 --> 00:15:46.825
‎Quack, quack, quack!
‎The ducks are bathing in the canal

00:15:46.905 --> 00:15:51.385
‎Eyes wide open,
‎looking at the fish and shrimp

00:15:51.465 --> 00:15:54.625
We did it! Great job!

00:16:09.385 --> 00:16:12.145
Shall we go on this ride?

00:16:30.585 --> 00:16:31.425
Ms. Lin.

00:16:34.985 --> 00:16:37.345
Having more fun than the kids?

00:16:38.545 --> 00:16:41.385
How did you know?
How long have you been here?

00:16:42.385 --> 00:16:45.185
Long enough
to see someone sing the duck song.

00:16:45.785 --> 00:16:46.825
Ms. Lin!

00:16:50.785 --> 00:16:55.065
I've talked with Mr. Pao.
Thank you so much for backing down.

00:16:56.465 --> 00:16:57.625
Right.

00:16:57.705 --> 00:16:59.185
Mr. Pao promised

00:16:59.265 --> 00:17:02.505
that he won't let anyone lose their job.
Everyone will have new jobs,

00:17:03.905 --> 00:17:05.745
because he's friends with the owner.

00:17:08.785 --> 00:17:10.545
I made him an offer

00:17:10.625 --> 00:17:12.825
that he has one month left
before we close down the park.

00:17:14.145 --> 00:17:15.385
One full month?

00:17:19.025 --> 00:17:21.184
So everyone has time to prepare.

00:17:21.905 --> 00:17:24.265
Both the staff and little kids.

00:17:25.704 --> 00:17:27.145
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

00:17:27.745 --> 00:17:30.345
You're the loveliest.

00:17:30.945 --> 00:17:32.585
Is this all the thanks I get?

00:17:33.545 --> 00:17:36.145
I have to present this matter
at the board meeting too.

00:17:36.225 --> 00:17:37.945
No reward for me at all?

00:17:54.905 --> 00:17:55.865
That's all?

00:18:27.585 --> 00:18:28.985
Ms. Lin!

00:18:29.065 --> 00:18:30.905
You're cheating right now.

00:18:33.625 --> 00:18:37.545
And don't you have
any consolation for someone

00:18:37.625 --> 00:18:39.905
who suddenly lost her job?

00:18:52.465 --> 00:18:54.345
That's enough, Ms. Lin.

00:18:59.065 --> 00:19:01.225
Silly. Let go.

00:19:14.945 --> 00:19:18.545
Walking with me this far is fine.
You can get back to work.

00:19:18.625 --> 00:19:19.705
Mhm.

00:19:20.465 --> 00:19:23.505
Then I'll treat you to
Japanese food again this evening, okay?

00:19:26.105 --> 00:19:27.145
Are you tired of it yet?

00:19:28.905 --> 00:19:32.505
I don't get tired of things. Once I pick
a favorite, it stays a favorite forever.

00:19:32.585 --> 00:19:34.065
I won't change my mind so easily.

00:19:35.225 --> 00:19:37.865
Okay. So, deal?

00:19:38.465 --> 00:19:39.385
Mhm.

00:19:46.545 --> 00:19:48.905
Ms. Lin, let's head back now.

00:21:10.785 --> 00:21:12.105
Looks so delicious.

00:21:15.345 --> 00:21:17.385
I wish you were here like this every day.

00:21:29.865 --> 00:21:31.465
The table's ready.

00:21:35.585 --> 00:21:37.305
I'm digging in!

00:21:40.025 --> 00:21:41.185
Ms. Lin.

00:21:43.585 --> 00:21:44.745
Come on.

00:21:48.665 --> 00:21:50.025
Gyoza time.

00:22:06.665 --> 00:22:07.665
Is it good?

00:22:12.065 --> 00:22:14.865
I knew Family Nest
from the wedding studio.

00:22:16.625 --> 00:22:18.785
That was our first business.

00:22:18.865 --> 00:22:23.785
Then we expanded into baby clothes,
maternity wear, toys, baby products,

00:22:23.865 --> 00:22:25.745
and much more.

00:22:26.865 --> 00:22:29.225
Then the tutoring school
will be something entirely new.

00:22:30.585 --> 00:22:33.385
Not that new. I'd say it's a continuation.

00:22:34.065 --> 00:22:36.745
We take care of our customers
from newlyweds to parenthood.

00:22:38.945 --> 00:22:41.985
So the tutoring school is for their kids?

00:22:42.745 --> 00:22:43.625
Yes.

00:22:44.185 --> 00:22:46.625
Parents want
the best schools for their kids,

00:22:46.705 --> 00:22:48.785
so we aim to help prepare them.

00:23:13.705 --> 00:23:15.465
Smells so good.

00:23:17.225 --> 00:23:19.105
Don't touch it. It's still hot.

00:23:23.305 --> 00:23:25.385
Did you wash the dishes or wash your hair?

00:23:55.105 --> 00:23:56.025
Ms. Lin.

00:23:59.225 --> 00:24:00.905
Why are you taking so long?

00:24:02.145 --> 00:24:04.625
So this is what a "stunner" looks like.

00:24:10.785 --> 00:24:12.825
Is it so hard to wipe it?

00:24:17.625 --> 00:24:18.785
Can we eat now?

00:24:19.425 --> 00:24:20.905
-Wanna taste it?
-Mhm.

00:24:31.865 --> 00:24:32.945
Is it good?

00:24:34.025 --> 00:24:35.745
-No.
-Oh?

00:24:36.345 --> 00:24:37.185
Just kidding.

00:24:37.265 --> 00:24:38.785
It's delicious.

00:24:47.385 --> 00:24:49.225
The best I've ever tasted.

00:24:51.625 --> 00:24:52.785
You eat it.

00:24:55.185 --> 00:24:56.185
Delicious?

00:25:02.585 --> 00:25:04.465
I want to hear more about you too.

00:25:07.505 --> 00:25:09.625
There's nothing interesting about me.

00:25:10.465 --> 00:25:12.945
I don't care what others think,
but I'm interested.

00:25:17.425 --> 00:25:18.825
What do you want to know?

00:25:20.785 --> 00:25:21.985
About Donut.

00:25:24.425 --> 00:25:25.385
I knew it.

00:25:25.465 --> 00:25:29.305
I was so shocked
to find out you have a child.

00:25:30.905 --> 00:25:33.105
You thought Ith was the father, right?

00:25:34.865 --> 00:25:36.025
Yeah.

00:25:37.465 --> 00:25:39.025
Everyone thinks that.

00:25:40.105 --> 00:25:42.025
I thought my intuition failed me there.

00:25:42.105 --> 00:25:43.665
I almost gave up on flirting with you.

00:25:46.265 --> 00:25:48.305
Why are you so direct?

00:25:50.185 --> 00:25:51.345
Not always.

00:25:52.745 --> 00:25:53.865
And…

00:25:55.385 --> 00:25:58.145
don't you mind that I have a child?

00:25:59.305 --> 00:26:01.785
Not at all. I love kids.

00:26:10.545 --> 00:26:12.625
Why are you saying it
like you're in a beauty pageant?

00:26:18.385 --> 00:26:21.225
If your family was still together,

00:26:21.305 --> 00:26:22.545
I would have stepped away.

00:26:38.705 --> 00:26:40.945
So it's not just me, right?

00:27:23.305 --> 00:27:24.305
I…

00:27:28.705 --> 00:27:30.465
I need to leave.

00:27:45.065 --> 00:27:46.985
I'm worried Ms. Lin
is being deceived, sir.

00:27:47.585 --> 00:27:49.665
But it didn't affect her work, right?

00:27:50.825 --> 00:27:52.305
Just a little delay.

00:27:52.385 --> 00:27:55.105
Ms. Lin postponed
the Play Park closure by a month

00:27:55.185 --> 00:27:58.145
to keep that woman happy.

00:28:02.865 --> 00:28:04.545
And what does the board say?

00:28:04.625 --> 00:28:06.025
I still haven't gotten an update.

00:28:06.105 --> 00:28:09.185
But Ms. Lin has scheduled a meeting
to clarify the progress and reason.

00:28:11.625 --> 00:28:13.345
Please take care of Lin for me.

00:28:14.105 --> 00:28:16.745
Don't let her personal matters
hinder the work.

00:28:18.705 --> 00:28:21.465
And if you see anything
that could be problematic,

00:28:22.145 --> 00:28:24.105
handle it immediately.

00:28:24.665 --> 00:28:25.865
You have my permission.

00:28:26.545 --> 00:28:27.665
Yes, sir.

00:28:36.705 --> 00:28:38.225
Ith!

00:28:38.305 --> 00:28:39.585
Again?

00:28:39.665 --> 00:28:41.825
Leave some lights on, please.

00:28:41.905 --> 00:28:43.465
The shock's going to kill me someday.

00:28:44.265 --> 00:28:46.785
And what's with you?
Aren't you going to sleep?

00:28:47.385 --> 00:28:48.425
Want a night guard job?

00:28:50.745 --> 00:28:51.625
I'm considering it.

00:28:54.305 --> 00:28:56.025
What's bugging you again?

00:28:57.705 --> 00:28:59.065
Can you stay out of it just once?

00:29:00.705 --> 00:29:03.425
No, because I have only one sister.

00:29:07.465 --> 00:29:09.145
Well, well.

00:29:09.985 --> 00:29:11.265
Relationship drama, for sure.

00:29:11.345 --> 00:29:12.665
Smartass.

00:29:12.745 --> 00:29:14.105
Did I get it right?

00:29:15.545 --> 00:29:16.385
Mhm.

00:29:19.865 --> 00:29:22.825
Do you remember Ms. Lin?

00:29:23.465 --> 00:29:25.105
-Really?
-I didn't say anything.

00:29:25.185 --> 00:29:26.545
Is she the one?

00:29:28.545 --> 00:29:29.385
Mhm.

00:29:29.985 --> 00:29:31.425
Go for it, sis.

00:29:31.505 --> 00:29:32.625
Are you crazy?

00:29:33.465 --> 00:29:34.545
Isn't it too soon?

00:29:34.625 --> 00:29:36.505
What's the holdup?

00:29:38.785 --> 00:29:41.745
You know I haven't been
in a relationship before.

00:29:41.825 --> 00:29:44.305
And look at her.

00:29:44.385 --> 00:29:46.345
Look at how experienced she is.

00:30:01.385 --> 00:30:03.785
There. Why are you blushing then?

00:30:04.305 --> 00:30:06.345
And your ears. All red.

00:30:13.305 --> 00:30:15.425
But I really don't know

00:30:15.505 --> 00:30:17.825
if this kind of love will last.

00:30:18.785 --> 00:30:21.745
I'm not sure if it's right for me.

00:30:22.785 --> 00:30:23.625
Well…

00:30:26.025 --> 00:30:27.265
I don't know.

00:30:27.825 --> 00:30:29.985
And I'm scared to move forward with it.

00:30:30.545 --> 00:30:32.545
I don't want anyone
to end up getting hurt.

00:30:33.225 --> 00:30:35.065
You're still scarred
from what Guy did, right?

00:30:37.785 --> 00:30:39.065
Listen to me.

00:30:39.985 --> 00:30:42.225
You need to erase
all those awful memories.

00:30:42.945 --> 00:30:44.305
It wasn't your fault.

00:30:45.945 --> 00:30:48.345
Also, it wasn't even your choice.

00:30:54.305 --> 00:30:55.585
Or is it because of Donut?

00:30:57.425 --> 00:30:58.265
No.

00:30:59.905 --> 00:31:01.825
He'll understand when he grows up.

00:31:03.625 --> 00:31:05.145
It's more like my problem.

00:31:17.225 --> 00:31:19.865
Ms. Lin! Ms. Lin.

00:31:20.465 --> 00:31:21.305
Ms. Lin.

00:31:23.825 --> 00:31:25.625
You forgot your bag.

00:31:26.785 --> 00:31:27.945
Thank you.

00:31:28.545 --> 00:31:29.745
No balloons today, Gib?

00:31:30.945 --> 00:31:32.945
I don't see any, ma'am.

00:31:33.545 --> 00:31:34.785
Did you order them?

00:31:35.545 --> 00:31:36.625
No.

00:31:39.825 --> 00:31:42.905
Would you like me to throw away
the deflated balloons in your room?

00:31:42.985 --> 00:31:45.185
No need. Keep them there.

00:31:46.065 --> 00:31:47.065
Yes, ma'am.

00:32:22.065 --> 00:32:25.225
I… I need to leave.

00:32:49.865 --> 00:32:51.465
No drinks delivered today?

00:32:52.145 --> 00:32:54.665
No. Did you order it?

00:32:54.745 --> 00:32:55.945
I'll go get it for you.

00:32:56.025 --> 00:32:57.105
It's okay.

00:33:00.305 --> 00:33:01.545
They probably forgot.

00:33:03.025 --> 00:33:05.705
They can't forget it.
Have you paid for it?

00:33:06.625 --> 00:33:08.465
Forget it. I'll be right back.

00:33:09.145 --> 00:33:10.705
But these documents need to be signed.

00:33:10.785 --> 00:33:11.705
I'll be back.

00:33:12.665 --> 00:33:16.105
Where are you going, Ms. Lin? Ms. Lin?

00:33:20.065 --> 00:33:21.865
Play Park, for sure.

00:33:24.705 --> 00:33:27.145
Just installed the tracker,
and I need it immediately.

00:33:27.225 --> 00:33:28.625
I'm sorry, Ms. Lin.

00:33:28.705 --> 00:33:31.265
Your father told me
to keep a close eye on you.

00:33:34.665 --> 00:33:35.625
How do I use this?

00:33:46.025 --> 00:33:49.625
"I'm coming over. We need to talk."

00:33:54.065 --> 00:33:55.785
You had to come see me here?

00:34:01.705 --> 00:34:03.225
-May. May.
-Yes?

00:34:03.305 --> 00:34:05.425
If Ms. Lin comes and asks to see me,

00:34:05.505 --> 00:34:08.744
just tell her I'm out on errands
and I'm not sure when I'll be back, okay?

00:34:08.824 --> 00:34:11.344
-Yes, Manager.
-Okay, thank you.

00:34:11.425 --> 00:34:13.505
Let's go. You wanna go on this ride?

00:34:13.585 --> 00:34:15.625
Alright, be careful.

00:34:15.705 --> 00:34:17.985
Slowly. Let's go!

00:34:18.065 --> 00:34:18.945
Excuse me.

00:34:19.545 --> 00:34:20.945
Hello, Ms. Lin.

00:34:21.025 --> 00:34:23.425
May I ask where the manager is?

00:34:23.505 --> 00:34:26.705
She told me to tell you she's not here.

00:34:28.665 --> 00:34:30.065
I don't know. I'm sorry.

00:34:45.744 --> 00:34:46.744
I'm sorry.

00:34:46.824 --> 00:34:48.304
I'm sorry.

00:34:56.865 --> 00:35:00.385
Excuse me.
Do you know which way Play Park is?

00:35:04.465 --> 00:35:05.985
She's already taken.

00:35:08.425 --> 00:35:10.465
Sorry, may I ask your name?

00:35:10.545 --> 00:35:11.465
My name's Lilin.

00:35:11.545 --> 00:35:12.385
Lilin.

00:35:12.465 --> 00:35:13.705
And you?

00:35:13.785 --> 00:35:14.705
I'm Atis.

00:35:15.745 --> 00:35:17.305
What brings you here, Ms. Lilin?

00:35:17.825 --> 00:35:19.505
I'm attending a business meeting here.

00:35:19.585 --> 00:35:21.945
-A business meeting at Play Park?
-Yes.

00:35:24.025 --> 00:35:25.225
The weather's nice today.

00:35:26.345 --> 00:35:27.545
Yeah?

00:35:28.185 --> 00:35:29.905
But it's so cloudy.

00:35:29.985 --> 00:35:32.905
This is perfectly chill.
It'd be too hot if it were sunny.

00:35:35.865 --> 00:35:37.265
Want to get coffee together?

00:35:37.345 --> 00:35:38.305
Of course.

00:35:46.665 --> 00:35:48.625
Have you been here often?

00:35:49.745 --> 00:35:52.865
Not really. I've been busy,
so I rarely come.

00:35:57.385 --> 00:35:59.265
Your order's ready.

00:35:59.865 --> 00:36:02.985
-A dark roast Americano for you, sir.
-Thank you.

00:36:03.065 --> 00:36:05.465
-And hot green tea for you, ma'am.
-Thank you.

00:36:14.985 --> 00:36:16.625
I need to head back to the office now.

00:36:16.705 --> 00:36:18.705
I have an urgent meeting this afternoon.

00:36:19.865 --> 00:36:21.745
Will I have a chance to see you again?

00:36:30.225 --> 00:36:34.425
You bought me a drink today,
so let me treat you to dinner.

00:36:37.025 --> 00:36:38.025
Gladly.

00:36:57.265 --> 00:36:58.305
Come here, come here.

00:36:59.225 --> 00:37:00.425
What did you hear?

00:37:01.185 --> 00:37:02.745
They're meeting for dinner, IngIng.

00:37:03.465 --> 00:37:04.505
Where? When?

00:37:05.905 --> 00:37:07.505
I know this restaurant.

00:37:07.585 --> 00:37:08.985
My friend works there too.

00:37:09.065 --> 00:37:11.145
It's a fancy place.

00:37:12.145 --> 00:37:14.305
Though, your boyfriend's

00:37:14.945 --> 00:37:17.945
so handsome.

00:37:20.985 --> 00:37:24.385
And she seems a little intense.

00:37:24.465 --> 00:37:25.345
Stop it.

00:37:26.345 --> 00:37:29.985
Don't talk about her like that.
You don't even know her.

00:37:31.345 --> 00:37:32.185
Here.

00:37:33.465 --> 00:37:34.305
Take this.

00:37:35.025 --> 00:37:38.905
And listen, don't say anything
that would bring her down.

00:37:39.625 --> 00:37:40.465
Get back to work now.

00:37:40.545 --> 00:37:41.785
I thought it'd be 200.

00:38:39.265 --> 00:38:40.585
Ms. Lin.

00:38:42.305 --> 00:38:43.305
Is everything alright?

00:38:44.785 --> 00:38:48.025
I can't find my car.
I'm sure I parked it here.

00:38:50.385 --> 00:38:51.745
Maybe it's in a different zone?

00:38:52.385 --> 00:38:53.745
The parking zones look the same.

00:38:58.105 --> 00:38:59.425
I'll help you look for it.

00:38:59.985 --> 00:39:02.625
So, what's the car's color
and license plate number?

00:39:02.705 --> 00:39:05.785
It's a white car, plate number 4KT50

00:39:05.865 --> 00:39:06.865
Okay.

00:39:21.505 --> 00:39:22.465
It's here, Ms. Lin.

00:39:24.905 --> 00:39:27.025
White car, 4KT50.

00:39:27.625 --> 00:39:30.265
So it is. Thank you so much.

00:39:30.345 --> 00:39:31.385
It's nothing at all.

00:39:33.185 --> 00:39:36.065
And please don't forget our dinner.

00:39:55.585 --> 00:39:57.905
Are you sure
you don't want to be an actor, Mr. Atis?

00:39:58.865 --> 00:40:00.065
I wouldn't go that far.

00:40:01.105 --> 00:40:04.465
If you can secure a date with Ms. Lin,
you're something else.

00:40:05.425 --> 00:40:07.185
I should thank Coach Jane.

00:40:07.265 --> 00:40:09.545
This is next-level planning.

00:40:09.625 --> 00:40:11.065
How did you come up
with the parking spot trick?

00:40:11.665 --> 00:40:14.225
I always have
a spare key to her car with me.

00:40:14.305 --> 00:40:17.665
If I told her it was a blind date,
she would never agree to go.

00:40:17.745 --> 00:40:19.345
It had to be a coincidence like this.

00:40:22.025 --> 00:40:25.585
But if she finds out,
won't she be really upset?

00:40:27.025 --> 00:40:30.345
No… I mean, no one would be left alive.

00:40:32.545 --> 00:40:35.865
So when is the first date?

00:42:15.185 --> 00:42:17.385
You look so beautiful today.

00:42:17.465 --> 00:42:18.585
Thank you.

00:42:18.665 --> 00:42:21.505
All the boys will be stunned.

00:42:22.265 --> 00:42:24.625
I'd rather stun the girls.

00:42:25.625 --> 00:42:26.585
Your car key.

00:42:50.625 --> 00:42:51.465
Oh?

00:42:53.025 --> 00:42:53.945
She already left?

00:43:02.145 --> 00:43:03.625
Is she dressed to impress
or dressed for war?

00:43:06.265 --> 00:43:07.185
What's this?

00:43:48.265 --> 00:43:49.145
Ms. Lin.

00:44:10.185 --> 00:44:12.705
Your boss has been busy lately?

00:44:14.585 --> 00:44:16.225
If I'm not mistaken,

00:44:16.305 --> 00:44:19.625
I think Ms. Lin is in love, sir.

00:44:24.625 --> 00:44:27.305
So, we're dating now, right?

00:44:30.985 --> 00:44:32.385
What would you like to order?

00:44:32.465 --> 00:44:34.625
Please give us a moment to decide.

00:44:37.105 --> 00:44:38.305
Prae?

00:46:36.225 --> 00:46:40.105
Subtitle translation by:
Anan Pratchayakul